About the job
Entry-Level Quality Assurance Engineer
We are seeking a detail-oriented and analytical Quality Assurance (QA) Engineer to join our team. The role focuses on ensuring the quality, reliability, and performance of software products through rigorous testing and validation. The ideal candidate will possess strong problem-solving skills, technical aptitude, and a keen eye for identifying defects and inconsistencies.
Key responsibilities include designing and executing test plans, documenting results, and collaborating with development teams to ensure software meets functional and performance requirements. The QA Engineer will participate in developing automated test scripts, tracking issues, and verifying fixes to maintain high standards of product quality. Strong familiarity with testing methodologies, software tools, and quality assurance processes is essential.
Effective communication skills are important for reporting findings clearly and collaborating across cross-functional teams. The role emphasizes attention to detail, analytical thinking, and a commitment to continuous improvement. Staying updated on emerging testing tools, frameworks, and best practices is a key component of success in this position.
This position provides an opportunity to contribute to the delivery of high-quality software, develop technical and analytical skills, and collaborate in a dynamic, innovation-driven environment. The QA Engineer will play a vital role in supporting the organization’s commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction.

